text.tspan: Name: Krok
Age: 33
Status: Detained
Role: Amalgam
Documentation:
Click this to exit
Harry was a chatterbox of sorts. There
was never a moment where he didn't
run his mouth. So we decided to do
the world a favour, and kidnap him.
We gave him a choice between two
options, remove his face or turn it
into a mouth. He chose option two.
We now have him in a containment
chamber, and our tests clearly worked,
as he hasnt spoken a word to anybody
who entered his chamber since the day
we turned him into this.
DONK
Industries
